As an organization that has been passed down since ancient times---guarding the peace of a world, Sering Palace should have been admired by the world, but several attacks have occurred in the past month. His curiosity eventually caused him to accidentally get involved in the investigation of the case, and bet on his future for this. In order to find the truth, Manduo decided to sneak into the Forbidden Book Pavilion in the Lingfu Palace, hoping to find a key clue. On the night of his action, he happened to encounter the mysterious invader Ye Chuangshu Pavilion. The invaders killed the elders who guarded the pavilion, took away the treasures passed down in the mansion, and set fire to the library. Mandu witnessed everything, followed the intruder all the way in hopes of regaining the treasure, but was teased by the intruder, and was eventually arrested as a suspect and sent to death row awaiting execution after trial and conviction. On the day of execution, Manduo went into madness between life and death, and burst out with unprecedented power. With this power, Manduo was able to escape. Manduo, who had been born after the escape, regained his senses, and learned that he had become a fugitive through his only friend, Afan, who was serving in the Ling Palace. When Afan brought the news, he also attracted the follow-up of Jing Jing, the daughter of the Lingfu Palace who hoped to catch many cases. title: URVAN
synopsis: The film is set in the city of Sasebo in Nagasaki prefecture.
background:
"URVAN" is set in Sasebo City, which was produced by Toei Animation's new IP research and development team "PEROs" with the cooperation of Nagasaki International University.
By utilizing remote location scouting and the latest communication tools, it is a work that challenged the production of animation during the Corona pandemic, creating a new charm of the area without going to Sasebo, which was the stage.

- What is "URVAN" -
"URVAN" is said to be the etymology of "Obon", that is, "Urabone".
It refers to the ancient Avestan word "Ulvane (soul)" around the 7th century BC.

This work, "URVAN", is a mysterious and somewhat nostalgic cyberpunk action that mixes "unusual" and "everyday" with the motif of Obon, which welcomes and sends out spirits in Sasebo City, Nagasaki Prefecture.

The actual scenery of Sasebo expressed as an animation changes into the world of cyberpunk, and two mysterious men and women run through the mysterious city.
In addition, throughout the entire story, a number of Sasebo's representative special products are also colored in the video, expressing them in a "pointed" and "shining" form so that even locals can enjoy them freshly.

synopsis: "I'm going to live for myself!" The greatest assassin on Earth knew only how to live as a tool for his employers—until they stopped letting him live. Reborn by the grace of a goddess into a world of swords and sorcery, he's offered a chance to do things differently this time around, but there's a catch...He has to eliminate a super-powerful hero who will bring about the end of the world unless he is stopped. Now known as Lugh Tuatha Dé, the master assassin certainly has his hands full, particularly because of all the beautiful girls who constantly surround him. Lugh may have been an incomparable killer, but how will he fare against foes with powerful magic?  (Source: Yen Press)

synopsis: The story revolves around the life of a group of Przewalski's gazelle by the Qinghai Lake. In their ethnic group, there is a legend of "God of Fire", and no one dared to cross the boundary and enter the "Territory of God of Fire". When attacked by a pack of wolves, Mo Ji, the lamb, had nowhere to escape and entered the legendary forbidden area, met with the family of human scientist Luo Renping, and became good friends with his daughter Luo Jingjing. In the process of living with humans He gradually understood the true face of the "God of Fire". In the end, Mo Ji, the lamb, helped his own tribe with the help of human wisdom, defeated the wolves, and created his own miracle.  (translated from acfun)

He tells Eve "I fell in love with you," and without saving the courting begins. (Source: MAL News)

synopsis: The film tells the story of a middle school student Chen Tianle who accidentally entered a book of "Lovely China" in the experience of the virtual library, returning to the era when the hero Fang Zhimin grew up and lived, and turned into Fang Zhimin's side during his growth. Different roles have witnessed how the admired heroes are developed step by step. This animated work with the theme of reflecting the revolutionary hero Fang Zhimin evoked a lot of social response once it was broadcast. From the perspective of contemporary young people, this film shows the life of the patriotic hero Fang Zhimin and the "Chinese Dream" he fought for, inspiring young people to establish ideals and beliefs from an early age and continue to pursue and realize the Chinese dream in the new era.  (translated from bilibili)

On the surface, they are guests, but in fact they come with their own little nine or nine, or share with MOCO, or come to seek a solution, or simply come. kill time. synopsis: In order to solve the earth’s energy crisis, the Purcell is on the mission of discovering new energy in space. In mission after mission, it has delivered precious cosmic data and clean energy to the earth. Now the protagonist SPT team will start a new one. Explore the adventure, where will their next destination be? During the voyage, the Purcell was blocked by a kind of enchantment called "Ice". In order to open the enchantment, the SPT vanguard team came to Ice and Snow Star, where they will encounter the mysterious big snow monster, the giant bear star There is a magnet that records the true mystery of endless energy. In order to prevent the space pirates from making the first step, the Purcell assembled the God of War alliance, and they met the mysterious ultimate opponent! In the end, can they win and find endless energy?  (translated from iqiyi)
